{"id":"harodite","term":"Harodite","source":"Easton's Bible Dictionary (M.G. Easton, 1897)","html":"<p>An epithet applied to two of David’s heroes (<a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"2 Samuel 23:25\">2 Sam. 23:25</a>). (Comp. <a class=\"ref\" data-ref=\"1 Chronicles 11:27\">1 Chr. 11:27</a>.)</p>\n\u0000","refs":["2 Samuel 23:25","1 Chronicles 11:27"]}